
## Prerequisites
1. AWS Account with CLI configured
2. AWS CLI installed and configured
3. Existing EC2 Key Pair
4. Git (for cloning repository)

## Deployment Methods

### Method 1: CloudFormation (Recommended)
```bash
# Update parameters.json with your KeyName and IP
# Deploy stack
aws cloudformation create-stack \
  --stack-name resume-website \
  --template-body file://infrastructure/ec2-resume-cloudformation.yaml \
  --parameters file://infrastructure/parameters.json \
  --capabilities CAPABILITY_IAM

# Check status
aws cloudformation describe-stacks --stack-name resume-website

# Get website URL
aws cloudformation describe-stacks \
  --stack-name resume-website \
  --query "Stacks[0].Outputs[?OutputKey=='WebsiteURL'].OutputValue" \
  --output text
